title: Monday Post Show (3-5-21)
itunes:title: Monday Post Show (3-5-21)
description:
Bobby talks about Bhad Bhabie who broke the record of making the most on OnlyFans in 1 day. Bobby also talks about Raymundo who made a Cameo for his birthday after Caitlin ordered it. Bobby said he wasn’t to impress with it. We break down how much Raymundo is making on Cameo. Morgan2 also talks about going to Bonnaroo. Bobby also talks about how things will open up once we get the vaccine. Plus, Toi who used to run the iHeart Nashville front desk calls to wish Bobby a belated Happy Birthday!
